<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text">
      Remember, every verse carries its reward
    </h2>

    <blockquote class="mt-8 p-8 bg-background rounded-2xl">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text font-medium italic leading-relaxed">
        &ldquo;Whoever recites a letter of the Qur'an, he will have a reward, and the reward will be multiplied by ten. I do not say 'Alif, Lam, Meem' is one letter, but Alif is a letter, Lam is a letter, and Meem is a letter.&rdquo;
      </p>
      <footer class="mt-4 text-text-muted">
        &mdash; Sahih al-Tirmidhi 2910
      </footer>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>
